   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-" mid="51" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka seems to be in a serious mood.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-a" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Welcome, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. Have you made up your mind?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-a" image="QW_Merca_Heart.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-b" mid="53" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Yes. Merca is in trouble, and if I leave now to find the Chalice of Healing, I won't be proud of myself.<BR>I've received so much help from Vernicka, Sarrah, and many other people in this city and it's time to return the favour.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-b" image="QW_Merca_Heart.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-c" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It's not that I will give up on the chalice. I just want to do whatever I can to ensure Merca's safety or at the very least, earn it some time.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-d" mid="61" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Very well. I must make plans too then. Since you've decided to help, it would be better to get it done perfectly and make Merca a full-fledged member of the Anti-Goddess Faction.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-e" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…! Norfe, you're going to help Merca too?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-f" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Not just me but the entire Anti-Goddess Faction.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Norfe smiles.)</FONT> We still have time until <FONT color=#086171>Aergal Kingdom</FONT> gets back to us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-g" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>That would be more efficient and better aligned with the Anti-Goddess Faction's mission…To be honest, I wouldn't feel comfortable forsaking Merca when it needs help.<BR>I hope my master doesn't scold me in heaven.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-h" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>But still… Thank you so much, Norfe…….</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-h" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2" mid="55" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you don't need to thank me.<BR>Anyway, can you check on <FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT>'s thoughts? He must have one or two plans up his sleeve.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-" mid="56" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>In the meanwhile, I'll inform Grele and the rest.<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, please go to Merca Headquarters and ask <FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT> what he intends to do next.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="67" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>…You seriously don't know how to hide your expressions.<BR>It's written all over your face that you know everything already. Well, it would be hard not to know with that slave of the goddess making such a din.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'm sorry I overheard your conversation. But I came to offer my help.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="69" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9805_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Offer your help? Only now?<BR>You know very well how Merca lost its neutrality in the first place.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9805_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I don't need your help. As Edart's messenger has said, the only way Merca can survive is a peaceful annexation by a Child.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="QN_Hirendel.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9805_qu_03.ogg}<BR>That means I should negotiate with <FONT color=#a82424>Child Hirendel</FONT> whose territory is the closest to Merca. However, if the negotiations fail, we need to find another favourable Child while keeping Hirendel's attention away. Do you think you have a role to play in such diplomatic maneuvers?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Surrender to a Child…? That would make Merca as good as nothing. That's not what you really want! </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Then can you offer me another choice?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka's voice is icy cold.)</FONT> Go on, I'm all ears.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Goddess Vestinel could have terminated Merca's neutrality to manage the balance of the world with her own hands. In that case, even if Merca is peacefully taken over by a Child, it wouldn't ensure its safety.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>The goddess will turn the tides any time at her whim. So… you should join hands with the Anti-Goddess Faction instead. Lord Norfe just told me that he would provide all the support to help Merca regain its stability.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Wow, I must have influenced you a lot. Now you've become as eloquent as me. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka seems speechless.)</FONT><BR>I know a peaceful annexation isn't a perfect solution, but there's no other way.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" mid="77" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9805_qu_04.ogg}<BR>I know Anti-Goddess Faction's military power or technology cannot save Merca. However, the faction does know several Child lords who can act as a backup plan when negotiation with Hirendel fails. So I'll partly accept your offer.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9805_qu_05.ogg}<BR>Tell Lord Norfe that I accept his offer. But I will still try to negotiate with Childs. I believe that's reasonable enough.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I just want Merca to be safe. I know you want the same so I have no issues about that.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="QN_Nophee.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-" mid="81" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Now you can stop wasting my time and go back to Lord Norfe.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka has accepted the offer. Return to </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Norfe</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> and tell him about it.)</FONT> </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-a" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>What did Vernicka say?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-b" mid="57" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Tell him about your conversation with Vernicka.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-c" mid="58" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-!next" mid="59" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Hmm… That's what I expected. I understand his intentions but as you've said, becoming a subordinate of a Child wouldn't solve the problem at its roots.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
